data.description: Make this Holiday Builders EVERETT model your new home!  This lovely home overlooking the lakes features include open concept floorplan with a massive owner's suite and a huge walk-in closet. Upgrades include 42'' upper kitchen cabinetry, granite countertops and under-cabinet lighting, center island and breakfast bar.  Enhanced vinyl plank flooring in all main living areas with carpeted bedrooms. The uge covered and screened lanai extends the living space and is wonderful to relax and enjoy the lake view and evening sunsets!Saw Mill Creek a new community which boasts a clubhouse house and community pool!  Transferable 10-year Centricity limited structural warranty.
